quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,Kee bududet yan Nabiyow
  74,2,Ugutaay sinam Yallih digaalák meesis
  74,3,Kaadu isi Rabbi eyneb
  74,4,Kaadu isi sara najaasak saytunnos
  74,5,Kaadu Yallat agleyta haanam kee raqqate umaaneenak exxer
  74,6,Kaadu tu edde tassamgguh acwa maabin
  74,7,Kaadu ku Rabbih kacanu edde geytu waytaamal isbir
  74,8,Tokkel ugut Baantá fooximtu wayta waqdi
  74,9,Too ayró gibdi ayró
  74,10,Too ayró korosul xabcá mali
  74,11,Nabiyow! Yoo kee inâ bagut dibuk anuk gineh an num (waliid ibnul mughiira kinnuk) sittah cab
  74,12,Kaadu maggo maalu kah ecee num
  74,13,Kaadu kaallih geytimta xaylo kah ecee num
  74,14,Addunyal mano xabbacoysiyyah kah xabbacoyseeh farakka kah hee num
  74,15,Tohuk lakal xalay kee maalu kaah ossam qaagitaah sangeela
  74,16,"Caagid usuk elle yakkale inna hinna, diggah usuk naayoota cirdih angadduk suge"
  74,17,Saytutticin qaley girák tani yawqeemih kaa dirkiseyyo
  74,18,"Diggah usuk isi nafsil cubbuseeh, massoyseh Nabii kee Qhuraan xagitik iyyuwaam"
  74,19,Tokkel usuk abbarsimehik mannal massoysee ta uma xagit
  74,20,Tohuk lakal abbarsimehik mannal massoyseeh ta uma xagit
  74,21,Tohuk lakal usuk cubbii kee malat qagteh
  74,22,Tohuk lakal ceereeh fooca kaxxa ribiyyah ribe
  74,23,"Tohuk lakal cakkit derre cabeeh, kaxxamariiniteh"
  74,24,"Tokkel Qhuraanak: ah tu hinna Mucammad naharsi marak baahe baab akke waytek iyye"
  74,25,Ah tu hinna seehadâ maxcó akke waytek iyye
  74,26,"Saqhar deqsitta girá kaa culseyyo, teetit cararaah tet digaalá tammoysuh"
  74,27,Saqhar kinni girá maca koo tiysixxigeeh
  74,28,"Is xagaral cado macabtaay, lafa macabta carrissa tet akke waytek"
  74,29,"Is xagar carissaah, dattossah"
  74,30,Taban kee sagaal tet amol yan malaykak
  74,31,"Kaadu girá dacrisa mara malayka akke waytek maabinnino, Kaadu maabinnino ken ixxu koroosite marah aqayyaareey, kitab kah yontocowwime mari yasmitê gideh iyyaanam akke waytek, kaadu yeemene mari iimaan elle ossituuy, kitab kah yontocowwime maraa kee moominiin elle agaywaagite waytu, kaadu sorkocobbaxittet biyak le maraa kee koros Yalli tahat ceelalloh maca faxee ittuh, Tonnaah Yalli isih faxe mara makkoysaah isih faxe mara tirri haa, ku Rabbih qandé takkeh gide taaxigê matan kaa akke waytek, girá tu hinna is seehadah kassis takkemkeh iyyaanam akke waytek"